  "tosSection2Para2": "You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for すべて activities that occur under your account. Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.",
  "tosSection3Title": "健康 Information — Not Medical Advice",
  "tosSection3Para1": "{appName} is a 健康 companion application intended for informational and organizational purposes only. The Service is NOT a medical device and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendations.",
  "tosSection3Para2": "The AI トリアージ feature provides general guidance based on the 症状 you report. It is not a substitute for professional medical judgment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you read in this Service.",
  "tosSection3Para3": "In a medical e緊急 call your local 緊急 number (e.g. 911, 112) immediately. Do not rely on the Service for 緊急 response.",
  "tosSection4Title": "本サービスの利用",
  "tosSection4Intro": "お客様は、以下の行為を行わないことに同意するものとします：",
  "tosSection4Bullet1": "本サービスを違法な目的で使用すること；",
  "tosSection4Bullet2": "本アプリのリバースエンジニアリング、逆コンパイル、または逆アセンブルを試みること；",
