  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to その他 users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "本サービスを利用して、未承諾の通信やスパムを送信すること。",
  "tosSection5Title": "定期購読と支払い",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"Pプロ or \"Eエンタープライズ plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective t利用規約",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or キャンセル your subscription at any 時間 through your platform's account s設定",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will ではない apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "お客様のデータ",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the 健康 data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our プライバシー Policy, which is incorporated into these 利用規約 by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may エクスポート your data at any 時間 via the in-app エクスポート feature, and you may permanently 削除 your account and すべて associated data via 設定 → 削除 Account.",
  "tosSection7Title": "免責事項",
  "tosSection7Para1": "本サービスは、「現状有姿」かつ「利用可能な状態」で提供され、明示・黙示を問わず、いかなる種類の保証も付随せず、 明示か黙示かを問わず、商品性、特定目的への適合性、または権利侵害の不存在に関する黙示の保証を含みますが、これらに限定されません。",
  "tosSection7Para2": "We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure, or that the AI トリアージ recommendations will be accurate or appropriate for your specific situation.",
  "tosSection8Title": "責任の制限",
  "tosSection8Para1": "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN いいえ EVENT SHALL {producer} BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR USE OF (OR INABILITY TO USE) THE SERVICE, WHETHER BASED ON WARRANTY, CONTRACT, TORT, OR ANY その他 LEGAL THEORY.",
  "tosSection9Title": "解約",
  "tosSection9Para1": "You may stop using the Service and 削除 your account at any 時間 via S設定 We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service if you violate these 利用規約 or if we reasonably believe we are 必須 to do so by law.",
  "tosSection9Para2": "Upon termination, すべて licenses granted to you will end, and your data will be deleted in accordance with our プライバシー Policy.",
